OL,6,FUTV can reveal that two firefighters
OL,7,Fhave been dismissed in a scandal
OL,8,Frocking the Northern Ireland Fire
OL,9,FService. The focus - the Southern Area
OL,10,FCommand headquarters in Portadown.
OL,12,FAnd there's been more than one
OL,13,Finvestigation into claims of serious
OL,14,Fmisconduct in the organisation. One of
OL,15,Fthem is still ongoing.
OL,17,FThere are allegations and claims of
OL,18,Fserious misconduct ` including
OL,19,Fdrinking on the job ` and allegations
OL,20,Fof bullying and harassment.
