OL,6,FUTV understands two firefighters have
OL,7,Fbeen recently dismissed - they have 28
OL,8,Fdays to appeal the decision.
OL,10,FWe can also reveal there is a separate
OL,11,Fwider investigation still ongoing into
OL,12,Fallegations of bullying and harassment
OL,13,Fand that several other crew are off on
OL,14,Flong-term sick.
OL,16,FNIFRS provided a statement on the
OL,17,Finvestigation that has just concluded
OL,18,F` but not the one ongoing.
