OL,6,FA NIFRS Spokesperson said: "A robust
OL,7,Finternal investigation into
OL,8,Fallegations of misconduct at Portadown
OL,9,FFire Station has concluded. The
OL,10,Fappropriate action has been taken in
OL,11,Fline with NIFRS policy. We do not
OL,12,Fcomment on individual employee
OL,13,Fmatters. Ongoing support is being
OL,14,Fprovided.
OL,16,F"We want to reassure the local
OL,17,Fcommunity that an effective emergency
OL,18,Fresponse in the Portadown area is
OL,19,Fbeing maintained. Your Fire & Rescue
OL,20,FService is ready to respond when you
OL,21,Fneed us most."
